Scope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.32</biblScope></bibl></cit>, etc., and <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">εἴ τις καὶ ἄ.</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg006.perseus-grc1:1:4:15\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ An.\">An.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.4.15</biblScope></bibl></cit>, etc., <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">v.</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">εἰ</ref></xr>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n4490.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> freq. with another of its own cases or derived Adverbs, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἄ. ἄλλα λέγει</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">one man</tr_> says <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">one thing, one another</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg006.perseus-grc1:2:1:15\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ An.\">An.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.1.15</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἄ. ἄλλω᾽ ἔλεγεν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg011.perseus-grc1:220c\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Smp.\">Smp.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">220c</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἄ. ἄλλῃ ἐτράπετο</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg006.perseus-grc1:4:8:19\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ An.\">An.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.8.19</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">v.</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">ἄλλοθεν, ἄλλοσε, ἄλλοτε</ref> </xr>; also with Verb in pl., <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">παραλαμβάνων ἄ. ἄλλον ἐπ᾽ ἄλλου, τὸν δ᾽ ἐπ᾽ ἄλλου χρείᾳ . . ἐθέμεθα πόλιν ὄνομα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg030.perseus-grc1:369c\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ R.\">R.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">369c</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg007.perseus-grc1:2:1:4\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Cyr.\">Cyr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.1.4</biblScope></bibl>, etc.: pl., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἄλλοι</foreign> when the several parties are pl., <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">λείπουσι τὸν λόφον . . ἄλλοι ἄλλοθεν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg006.perseus-grc1:1:10:13\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ An.\">An.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.10.13</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n4490.3\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἄ. καὶ ἄ.</foreign>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">one and then another, one or two</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg006.perseus-grc1:1:5:12\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ An.\">An.</a></