> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οἵτε ἄλλοι καί</foreign>. . <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">all others</tr_> and especially . . , <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">γυναῖκας ἄλλας τε πολλὰς καὶ δὴκαὶ βασιλέος θυγατέρα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.1</biblScope></bibl></cit>, etc.; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἄλλα τε δὴ εἶπε, καί</foreign>. . <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg006.perseus-grc1:142c\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Tht.\">Tht.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">142c</biblScope> </bibl>; (v. <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἄλλως</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg006.perseus-grc1:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>):—<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὸ ἄλλο</foreign> is much less freq. than <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὰ ἄλλα</foreign>. </sense> <sense n=\"7\" id=\"n4490.7\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> with Numerals, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">yet, still, further</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τρίτον ἄ. γένος</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0020.tlg002.perseus-grc1:143\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hes.\">Hes.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Op.\">Op.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">143</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">πέμπτος ποταμὸς ἄ.</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">yet</tr_> a fifth river, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:gre